name: Ent's End
description:
Defeat Evil Company as Ent in this simple platformer with elements of action and puzzle. Your character is very slow, but you can think before getting out of safe zone. Walk through factory ROOMS, filled with sawblades. This deadly DISKS can destroy you in one-shot, so be carefull!

Get stuck on hard/bugged level? Use Cheat Codes combination: 

  1. X+C - Previous level
  2. X+V - Next Level
